<plot>NEW CHILDREN/NEW YORK looks at the current state of immigration through those affected most: immigrant children. Three youths, coming of age in Bushwick, a vastly immigrant Latino community in Brooklyn are observed. The documentary paints an intimate portrait of the daily struggles and triumphs of these children.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?394003</url></doc>
